'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 154''' is the one hundred fifty-second issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published in [[February]] [[1982]].

This issue includes one of the few original comic stories in the series, "[[Tilotny Throws a Shape]]". It was later reprinted and colorized in ''[[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds 2]]''.

==Contents==
*"[[Tilotny Throws a Shape]]"
